description: Ministry of City Planning and Water Supply - Order to approve the acquisition of the immovable properties in Chundakuli, Fort and Grand Bazaar, Jaffna D/S Division, Jaffna District for the constructions of Sewerage Pump House No. 05, No. 13 and No. 14 respectively under the Jaffna-Kilinochchi Water Supply & Sanitation Projectunder the Bulathkohupitiya Water Supply Scheme and under the Galigamuwa Water Supply Scheme respectively
